1 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 916, is
2 amended to read as follows:
3 Section 916. The following are the acts deemed to constitute
4 disturbance of a religious meeting as prohibited by Section 915 of
5 this title:
6 1. Uttering any profane discourse, committing any rude or
7 indecent act, or making any unnecessary noise, either within the
8 place where such meeting is held, or so near it as to disturb the
9 order and solemnity of the meeting.;
10 2. Exhibiting or engaging in, within one (1) mile, any shows or
11 plays protest, demonstration, show, or play without a license by the
12 proper authority.;
13 3. Engaging in, or aiding or promoting within the like
14 distance, any racing of animals or gaming of any description.; or
15 4. Obstructing in any manner, without authority of law, within
16 the like distance one (1) mile, the free passage along any highway
17 to the place of such the meeting.
18 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
19 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
20 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
21 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
